Package: sparklite
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight frontend to run R code on an Apache Spark cluster
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-08-25
Author: Clark Fitzgerald
Maintainer: Clark Fitzgerald <clarkfitzg@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    sparkapi
Suggests:
    testthat
Description: The smallest amount of code needed to run parallel R on an
    Apache Spark cluster through a direct interface with the Spark Java
    class org.apache.spark.api.r.RRDD. Function names and parameters are
    copied from R's parallel package.
License: MIT
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
